this case immediately

22:28.848 --> 22:32.048
on the grounds
that the defendant...

22:38.528 --> 22:41.628
Are you all right, Mr. Bradley?

22:45.465 --> 22:47.595
I'm sorry, your honor.
I just can't.

22:51.401 --> 22:53.849
I just can't.

22:53.873 --> 22:57.113
Mr. Bradley,
do you need a recess?

22:58.478 --> 23:00.386
What the hell's going on?

23:00.410 --> 23:03.429
David, where are you going?

23:03.453 --> 23:04.930
I'm sorry. I quit.

23:04.954 --> 23:07.438
You can't just quit
in the middle of a hearing.

23:07.462 --> 23:09.995
I'd love to get
your idiot husband out of jail,

23:10.019 --> 23:11.667
but I just can't do it. I'm
sorry. Yeah. Why not?

23:11.691 --> 23:13.368
Because I'm in love with you.

23:13.392 --> 23:14.870
What?

23:14.894 --> 23:17.578
The other day in the hospital,
I started to feel something.

23:17.602 --> 23:19.745
I don't know.
Maybe it was there all along.

23:19.769 --> 23:23.709
But when I look into your eyes,
I know you feel it, too.

23:23.733 --> 23:25.451
We belong together.

23:25.475 --> 23:26.752
Okay, David,

23:26.776 --> 23:29.455
