and shoot you myself.

23:33.443 --> 23:35.461
I can't.

23:35.485 --> 23:36.685
I'm sorry.

23:50.730 --> 23:52.560
Come in!

23:54.504 --> 23:56.442
We need to talk.

23:56.466 --> 23:58.744
Oh! Oh! Uh, uh...

23:58.768 --> 24:01.487
Paul, you... you can't just
waltz into people's houses.

24:01.511 --> 24:03.018
Susan, you told me to come in.

24:03.042 --> 24:05.020
Well, that's 'cause I assumed

24:05.044 --> 24:06.861
you were someone
I would let in my house.

24:06.885 --> 24:08.554
What do you want?

24:08.578 --> 24:11.527
I was looking through my mail,
and I found this.

24:11.551 --> 24:13.529
I was surprised to discover

24:13.553 --> 24:15.566
that you were looking
for my son.

24:15.590 --> 24:17.533
You didn't happen to find
anything out

24:17.557 --> 24:19.535
about where Zach might be,
did you?

24:19.559 --> 24:21.837
No. No, I didn't.

24:21.861 --> 24:24.570
Sorry I can't help you out.

24:24.594 --> 24:26.517
