if you remember,

24:26.541 --> 24:28.514
Zach hid here
in this house before,

24:28.538 --> 24:31.076
and now I learn that
you've been searching for him.

24:31.100 --> 24:33.549
Well, he's not here.

24:33.573 --> 24:35.080
Hmm.

24:35.104 --> 24:37.061
Well, maybe we should
double-check.

24:37.085 --> 24:40.055
But he's not here. I swear.

24:40.079 --> 24:42.209
What are you grabbing for?

24:44.483 --> 24:46.832
A knife.

24:46.856 --> 24:49.556
I just want to slice
some tomatoes.

24:57.967 --> 24:59.875
I don't know how I know this,

24:59.899 --> 25:01.929
but I-I think that he's in Utah.

25:03.803 --> 25:06.552
He... he took a bus to bountiful.

25:06.576 --> 25:08.236
You have family there, right?

25:10.509 --> 25:13.139
Okay, I gave him the bus fare.

25:26.996 --> 25:29.234
You might want to be
careful with that.

25:29.258 --> 25:31.528
You seem a little jittery.

25:38.768 --> 25:42.117
Look, I know the timing is bad.

25:42.141 --> 25:43.288
Pretty bad.

25:43.312 --> 25:44.790
I feel terrible.

25:44.814 --> 25:47.761
How was I supposed to know
that he would take a bullet

25:47.785 --> 25:50.696
and suddenly realize
he's in love with me?

25:50.720 --> 25:53.699
Okay, look, I know I pushed you
into hiring that creep,

25:53.723 --> 25:57.110
but I promise I will do
anything I can to fix this.

25:57.134 --> 26:00.706
All right, go have sex
with Bradley.

26:00.730 --> 26:01.837
What?

26:01.861 --> 26:04.640
Well, that's what you want me
to say, isn't it?

26:04.664 --> 26:07.748
God, you guys are good.
I mean, you set me up perfectly.

26:07.772 --> 26:10.716
You think David and I planned
this so we could sleep together?

26:10.740 --> 26:13.548
Let's see. The guy tells me
to my face that he wants

26:13.572 --> 26:16.259
to get into your pants,
quits a week before my trial,

26:16.283 --> 26:20.255
and now you can't wait
to doanythingto get him back?

26:20.279 --> 26:23.158
Yeah. I'd like to go back
to jail now.

26:23.182 --> 26:25.160
