26:25.184 --> 26:27.771
I have been nothing
but faithful to you!

26:27.795 --> 26:29.595
Since you've been in here.

26:29.619 --> 26:32.197
Save it.
I know when I've been outfoxed,

26:32.221 --> 26:35.200
and please don't pretend
that you're doing this for me,

26:35.224 --> 26:37.207
'cause I'd rather rot in here.
And you know what?

26:37.231 --> 26:39.204
A lesser woman
would let you rot in here,

26:39.228 --> 26:40.706
but I'm not gonna do that.

26:40.730 --> 26:42.708
I'm not gonna give you
the satisfaction.

26:42.732 --> 26:44.710
So you better start
packing up your shanks

26:44.734 --> 26:46.917
or whatever you people
make in here,

26:46.941 --> 26:49.106
because you're coming home
with me!

26:52.311 --> 26:54.311
I don't have any shanks.

26:58.688 --> 27:00.726
Good afternoon. Checking in?

27:00.750 --> 27:04.329
Yes. Reservations in the name
of Williams... George Williams.

27:04.353 --> 27:05.600
Let me get your paperwork.

27:05.624 --> 27:07.607
So what do you want to do first?

27:07.631 --> 27:10.105
I don't know. I thought maybe
we could go antiquing.

27:10.129 --> 27:12.678
I hear you have
some lovely museums nearby.

27:12.702 --> 27:14.309
Do you have any brochures?

27:14.333 --> 27:16.250
Right over there, Mrs. Williams.

27:16.274 --> 27:18.013
Oh, uh, she's not my wife.

27:18.037 --> 27:21.067
I'm so sorry.

27:25.014 --> 27:27.631
So I hear they have a terrific
farmers' market nearby.

27:27.655 --> 27:30.996
We should pick up
some nectarines.

27:31.020 --> 27:32.798
George...

27:32.822 --> 27:33.799
I can't.

27:33.823 --> 27:35.100
What?

27:35.124 --> 27:37.808
I can't stay in a hotel
room with you. Why not?

27:37.832 --> 27:40.005
Because I am starting
to get that rash again.

27:40.029 --> 27:42.207
Well, I brought
the antihistamines.

27:42.231 --> 27:43.709
Oh, please. It's not gonna help.

27:43.733 --> 27:45.720
George, clearly,
this is psychosomatic.

27:45.744 --> 27:47.713
We need to go home.

27:47.737 --> 27:50.175
Bree, we just drove
three hours to get here.

27:50.199 --> 27:52.377
I know, and you have
every right to be mad,

27:52.401 --> 27:54.379
but, George, I am really
starting to itch.

27:54.403 --> 27:55.881
