already.

30:23.853 --> 30:25.170
Oh, yeah.

30:25.194 --> 30:27.873
So I was talking to one
of the bellmen,

30:27.897 --> 30:30.876
and he said there's a place
not far from here

30:30.900 --> 30:32.938
where we could go
horseback riding.

30:32.962 --> 30:35.941
Doesn't that sound like fun?
George?

30:35.965 --> 30:38.944
Wh-what? What? I'm sorry.

30:38.968 --> 30:41.987
I was saying I think
we should go horseback riding.

30:42.011 --> 30:44.571
Oh, sure. That'd be great.

30:47.516 --> 30:48.593
What's wrong?

30:48.617 --> 30:49.594
Nothing.

30:49.618 --> 30:51.596
I-I just don't think
that we should risk

30:51.620 --> 30:53.158
