30:53.182 --> 30:55.909
Well, I'm not gonna get another
rash just by holding your hand.

30:55.933 --> 30:58.003
You never know.

30:58.027 --> 31:02.287
Oh. Well, okay.

31:06.395 --> 31:11.116
Hey, uh, I brought
those antihistamines with me.

31:11.140 --> 31:14.019
Maybe you should take a couple,
