31:14.043 --> 31:15.520
Oh, I'm drinking wine.

31:15.544 --> 31:19.191
I don't think you're supposed
to mix pills with alcohol.

31:19.215 --> 31:21.186
That's for people who are...

31:21.210 --> 31:23.188
Who are about to use
heavy machinery.

31:23.212 --> 31:26.436
