a forklift tonight, do you?

31:26.460 --> 31:28.433
Well, you're the pharmacist.

31:28.457 --> 31:30.265
If you think it's okay...

31:30.289 --> 31:31.559
I do.

31:50.909 --> 31:53.919
George, I can't feel my legs.

31:53.943 --> 31:55.926
I know, sweetheart.
Don't you worry.

31:55.950 --> 31:57.923
I'm gonna take you to your room,

31:57.947 --> 31:59.995
and then we're gonna
get you into bed. Okay.

32:00.019 --> 32:01.296
Is she going to be okay?

32:01.320 --> 32:03.999
Yeah, she's just had
a little too much wine.

32:04.023 --> 32:06.310
I don't think
it was the wine, George.

32:06.334 --> 32:09.004
I think it was
the antihistamines.

32:09.028 --> 32:12.198
She doesn't know what
she's... we're good, thank you.

32:18.707 --> 32:20.015
Oh.

32:21.440 --> 32:23.248
No, no, no, no, no.

32:23.272 --> 32:25.312
I'll get those. You just relax.

32:32.982 --> 32:35.969
I love you very much, Bree.
You know that, right?

32:35.993 --> 32:38.525
I know.

32:45.234 --> 32:47.272
And I want

32:47.296 --> 32:49.944
more than anything

32:49.968 --> 32:52.077
for you to love me back.

32:52.101 --> 32:56.081
Do you understand
what I'm saying?

32:56.105 --> 32:57.983
Bree?

33:28.537 --> 33:29.607
Hey there.

33:31.180 --> 33:33.218
How you feeling?

33:33.242 --> 33:36.691
Oh, okay.

33:38.387 --> 33:41.066
Have you been sitting there
all this time?

33:41.090 --> 33:43.368
I wanted to make sure
you were okay,

33:43.392 --> 33:45.400
so I stayed
and watched you sleep.

33:45.424 --> 33:49.174
