34:10.518 --> 34:12.518
that you don't want me
in your bed.

34:15.184 --> 34:16.634
George.

34:19.757 --> 34:21.735
I know what you want from me,

34:21.760 --> 34:23.737
and I thought I wanted
the same thing,

34:23.762 --> 34:29.574
but I keep getting
those rashes because...

34:29.598 --> 34:31.775
