34:31.800 --> 34:35.580
Makes sense, I guess.

34:35.603 --> 34:40.625
Can't you just be patient?

34:40.649 --> 34:43.128
Can't you wait
just a little bit longer?

34:43.152 --> 34:46.391
I've already waited
my whole life for you,

34:46.415 --> 34:48.393
and I can wait a little more.

34:48.417 --> 34:49.594
Mmm.

34:49.618 --> 34:52.297
But let's be honest.

34:52.321 --> 34:54.821
There's no guarantee
that you'll ever be ready.

34:57.094 --> 34:59.765
There's only so much rejection
I can take.

35:01.470 --> 35:04.209
So...

35:04.233 --> 35:06.111
I'll do my best,

35:06.135 --> 35:08.213
but... don't be surprised

35:08.237 --> 35:11.556
if one of these days
you wake up and...

35:11.580 --> 35:13.140
