35:15.644 --> 35:17.631
Well, I should get back
to my room,

35:17.655 --> 35:19.624
try to get a little sleep.

35:19.648 --> 35:22.148
The antique stores open at 10.

35:24.893 --> 35:29.103
George, wait.

35:29.127 --> 35:31.797
Please don't go.

35:40.669 --> 35:42.709
Stay here with me.

35:52.150 --> 35:54.229
But what if you get
another rash?

35:54.253 --> 35:59.233
Well, I'll just...
Have to get over it, won't I?

36:46.905 --> 36:48.783
Gabrielle?

36:48.807 --> 36:50.307
I got your call...

36:54.743 --> 36:56.221
Wow.

36:56.245 --> 36:57.862
Does this mean
what I think it means?

36:57.886 --> 37:01.226
There are
some ground rules first.

37:01.250 --> 37:03.320
I'm not leaving my husband.

37:04.453 --> 37:06.876
Carlos is looking at
spending eight years in jail

37:06.900 --> 37:09.334
because of my lapse of judgment
with the gardener.

37:09.358 --> 37:12.337
I can't let him rot in there.
I'd be filled with guilt.

37:12.361 --> 37:15.510
You could get him out
and then divorce him.

37:15.534 --> 37:20.245
Not an option.
I'm catholic, hence the guilt.

37:20.269 --> 37:23.688
So what are our options?

37:23.712 --> 37:26.391
This, us, stolen moments,

37:26.415 --> 37:28.393
seeing each other
whenever we can.

37:28.417 --> 37:30.417
Carlos never needs to know.

37:33.322 --> 37:34.422
No.

37:36.254 --> 37:38.471
I thought this was
what you wanted.

37:38.495 --> 37:41.666
I want all of you.

37:41.690 --> 37:43.308
All or nothing.

37:43.332 --> 37:47.302
Then it's nothing.

37:50.299 --> 37:54.619
So you won't get a divorce,
but you'll have an affair?

37:54.643 --> 37:58.883
I said I was catholic,
not a fanatic.

37:58.907 --> 38:02.627
You know, David,
you could tell me to stop.

38:02.651 --> 38:06.391
Just tell me to stop,
and I will,

38:06.415 --> 38:08.993
or you can have me right now...

38:09.017 --> 38:10.687
On my terms.

38:13.922 --> 38:15.400
All right.

38:17.396 --> 38:18.973
Ow! Ow! Ow!

38:18.997 --> 38:20.975
Ow! What are you doing?

38:20.999 --> 38:23.308
Making my point.

38:23.332 --> 38:24.949
You don't love me.

38:24.973 --> 38:26.611
Aah! Yes, I do.

38:26.635 --> 38:28.613
No. You just agreed
to an affair...

38:28.637 --> 38:31.756
A cheap, illicit affair
with the woman you "love."

38:31.780 --> 38:33.958
Carlos would never share me.

38:33.982 --> 38:35.960
He's looking
at eight years in prison

38:35.984 --> 38:38.971
because the mere thought of it
sent him into a violent rage.

38:38.995 --> 38:40.465
Thatis love.

38:40.489 --> 38:43.749
This is... this is just lust,
mixed with posttraumatic stress.

38:45.093 --> 38:47.010
I will see you in court
tomorrow at 10 A.M.

38:47.034 --> 38:49.334
And don't be late,

38:49.358 --> 38:51.928
or else I'll have you disbarred
for sexual harassment.

39:08.577 --> 39:11.496
I'd take it easy
with that snail poison.

39:11.520 --> 39:14.399
It's hell on your agapanthus.

39:14.423 --> 39:16.631
Thanks. I'll keep that in mind.

39:16.655 --> 39:18.833
Is that why you stopped by...

39:18.857 --> 39:21.506
Share a few gardening tips?

39:21.530 --> 39:25.670
Nobody wants you here, Paul,
especially me.

39:25.694 --> 39:28.373
I'm just a father
looking for his son.

39:28.397 --> 39:31.497
Oh, I know what you are.

39:32.741 --> 39:35.420
First, your girlfriend
tries to run me off

39:35.444 --> 39:37.731
with some crazy story
about sending Zach to Utah.

39:37.755 --> 39:40.525
Now you're here
trying to scare me away.

39:40.549 --> 39:43.379
So much for "love thy neighbor."

39:45.414 --> 39:47.541
Anyway, thanks for the advice.

39:47.565 --> 39:51.095
About my agapanthus, I mean.

39:51.119 --> 39:53.938
I'll make sure I send you some.

39:53.962 --> 39:56.732
What did Susan tell you?

39:59.598 --> 40:01.075
Oh!

40:01.099 --> 40:04.549
You look beautiful.

40:04.573 --> 40:06.560
Oh, you should really
consider wearing this

40:06.584 --> 40:08.583
when you marry Mike.

40:08.607 --> 40:10.515
We could make it
a family tradition.

40:10.539 --> 40:12.517
Why don't we both stop
getting divorced?

40:12.541 --> 40:14.819
That would be a nice
family tradition. Oh.

40:14.843 --> 40:17.992
Hey!

40:18.016 --> 40:20.525
I need to ask you
something important.

40:20.549 --> 40:22.497
Oh, my god!

40:22.521 --> 40:23.768
Aah! This is it!

40:23.792 --> 40:26.931
Oh! Let me get my camera.

40:26.955 --> 40:29.003
Oh, no, mom, stop!

40:29.027 --> 40:30.735
What is it?

40:30.759 --> 40:33.599
Did you give Zach money
to go to Utah?

40:35.964 --> 40:37.181
What?

40:37.205 --> 40:39.435
Yes or no.

40:41.540 --> 40:45.119
He was talking so much
about Julie.

40:45.143 --> 40:48.723
I tried to get him
to come home with me...

40:48.747 --> 40:50.625
I mean, to... to you,

40:50.649 --> 40:53.127
but he just kept going
on and on about her,

40:53.151 --> 40:54.629
and I got scared.

40:54.653 --> 40:57.133
Yes or no.

40:58.627 --> 41:00.127
Yes.

41:02.731 --> 41:05.870
Mike. Mike, I didn't do it
to hurt you.

41:05.894 --> 41:08.473
You've gotta believe me. I...

41:08.497 --> 41:10.745
I should have told you
right away. I know that.

41:10.769 --> 41:14.549
But you know now,
so can we please talk about it? No.

41:14.573 --> 41:15.850
Mike, stop.

41:15.874 --> 41:18.531
Susan, you said you wanted to
help me, and I believed you.

41:18.555 --> 41:20.525
That's it. We're done.

41:20.549 --> 41:21.849
No...

41:25.253 --> 41:28.563
No, no, no, no!

41:28.587 --> 41:30.565
I screwed up, okay?!

41:30.589 --> 41:33.568
I want to fix it!
Please let me fix it!

41:33.592 --> 41:36.841
Tell me how to fix it!

41:36.865 --> 41:40.525
Mike... I love you.

41:43.632 --> 41:45.580
Please, no, please.

41:46.835 --> 41:48.482
Please.

41:48.506 --> 41:51.255
No, Mike! Mike, please!

41:51.279 --> 41:53.518
Come back!

41:53.542 --> 41:56.821
Come back!

42:36.054 --> 42:40.705
Yes, every little girl
dreams of a big white wedding.

42:40.729 --> 42:42.707
But some dreams

42:42.731 --> 42:44.731
just don't come true.
